title: Ghosts - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 4/29/22
itunes:title: Ghosts - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 4/29/22
description:
George Noory and psychic medium Mary Ann Winkowski discuss her lifelong experiences communicating with earthbound spirits, visiting haunted theaters and cemeteries, and how she was asked to remove a curse on a baseball team that went on to win the World Series.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
